Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 16:45:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Deploy SPY-DER automatically on VPS self-update

remote-deploy.sh now clones/updates /opt/spy-der and pip-installs it into
the 0DTE venv whenever main is pulled, so the parallel panel activates via
the existing zerodte-update.timer with no manual SSH.
---
 deploy/SPY_DER_PARALLEL.md | 35 +++++++++++++++--------------------
 deploy/remote-deploy.sh    | 37 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 deploy/zerodte.env.example |  6 ++++++
 3 files changed, 58 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)

diff --git a/deploy/SPY_DER_PARALLEL.md b/deploy/SPY_DER_PARALLEL.md
index 4f713de..e969a22 100644
--- a/deploy/SPY_DER_PARALLEL.md
+++ b/deploy/SPY_DER_PARALLEL.md
@@ -3,31 +3,27 @@
 SPY-DER appears beside Legacy / V2 / V3 in the dashboard **Parallel decisions**
 panel and as a fourth independent paper ledger (`spy_der`).
 
-## Install on the VPS
+## Auto-deploy (preferred)
 
-```bash
-# Same venv the shadow runner uses
-sudo -u zerodte /opt/zerodte/venv/bin/pip install -e /opt/spy-der
-
-# Optional: standalone heartbeat publisher
-sudo cp /opt/spy-der/deploy/spy-der-shadow.service /etc/systemd/system/
-sudo systemctl enable --now spy-der-shadow.service
-```
+The VPS `zerodte-update.timer` already pulls `0DTE` `main` every ~2 minutes
+and runs `remote-deploy.sh`. That script now also:
 
-Clone / sync SPY-DER to `/opt/spy-der` (or your preferred path) and keep it
-updated with `main`.
+1. Fast-forwards `/opt/spy-der` to `SPY-DER` `main`
+2. `pip install -e /opt/spy-der` into `/opt/zerodte/venv`
+3. Restarts shadow + dashboard
 
-## Environment
+So once this branch is **merged to 0DTE `main`**, the scanner picks up the
+parallel panel with no manual VPS SSH.
 
-Add to `/etc/zerodte/zerodte.env` when you want live Grok decisions:
+Optional Grok key in `/etc/zerodte/zerodte.env`:
 
 ```bash
 XAI_API_KEY=...
-# optional model override is owned by SPY-DER GrokConfig / deployment manifest
 ```
 
-Without `XAI_API_KEY`, SPY-DER falls back to the deterministic ensemble agent
-so the parallel panel still updates every tick.
+Without it, SPY-DER uses the deterministic agent so the panel still updates.
+
+Disable with `SPY_DER_ENABLED=0` in the deploy environment if needed.
 
 ## What you should see
 
@@ -40,8 +36,7 @@ Live broker routing remains disabled. This is paper/shadow comparison only.
 ## Rollback
 
 ```bash
-# Disable SPY-DER package import (track shows UNAVAILABLE)
-sudo -u zerodte /opt/zerodte/venv/bin/pip uninstall -y spy-der
-
-# Or roll the 0DTE checkout back before the parallel-track PR
+# Roll 0DTE main back before the parallel-track commit (self-update will follow),
+# or temporarily:
+sudo SPY_DER_ENABLED=0 bash /opt/zerodte/deploy/remote-deploy.sh
 ```
diff --git a/deploy/remote-deploy.sh b/deploy/remote-deploy.sh
index 8126a39..28c3ad2 100755
--- a/deploy/remote-deploy.sh
+++ b/deploy/remote-deploy.sh
@@ -22,6 +22,11 @@ ENV_FILE=/etc/zerodte/zerodte.env
 DATA_DIR=/var/lib/zerodte
 SVC=zerodte-shadow
 SVC_USER=zerodte
+# SPY-DER System B — parallel paper/dashboard track (paper/shadow only).
+SPY_DER_REPO_URL="${SPY_DER_REPO_URL:-https://github.com/DGator86/SPY-DER.git}"
+SPY_DER_DIR="${SPY_DER_DIR:-/opt/spy-der}"
+SPY_DER_REF="${SPY_DER_REF:-main}"
+SPY_DER_ENABLED="${SPY_DER_ENABLED:-1}"
 
 log() { printf '\n\033[1;36m==>\033[0m %s\n' "$*"; }
 
@@ -65,6 +70,38 @@ fi
 "$APP_DIR/venv/bin/pip" install --quiet --upgrade pip
 "$APP_DIR/venv/bin/pip" install --quiet -r "$APP_DIR/requirements.txt"
 
+if [ "$SPY_DER_ENABLED" = "1" ]; then
+    log "SPY-DER parallel track -> $SPY_DER_REF"
+    if [ ! -d "$SPY_DER_DIR/.git" ]; then
+        git clone "$SPY_DER_REPO_URL" "$SPY_DER_DIR"
+    fi
+    git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" remote set-url origin "$SPY_DER_REPO_URL"
+    git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" fetch --prune origin
+    if git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" rev-parse --verify -q "origin/${SPY_DER_REF#origin/}^{commit}" >/dev/null \
+       && [[ "$SPY_DER_REF" != origin/* ]]; then
+        SPY_TARGET="origin/$SPY_DER_REF"
+    elif git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" rev-parse --verify -q "${SPY_DER_REF}^{commit}" >/dev/null; then
+        SPY_TARGET="$SPY_DER_REF"
+    else
+        SPY_TARGET="origin/main"
+    fi
+    # Normalize: accept "main" or "origin/main"
+    if git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" rev-parse --verify -q "origin/main^{commit}" >/dev/null; then
+        if [[ "$SPY_DER_REF" == "main" ]]; then
+            SPY_TARGET="origin/main"
+        elif [[ "$SPY_DER_REF" == origin/* ]]; then
+            SPY_TARGET="$SPY_DER_REF"
+        elif git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" rev-parse --verify -q "origin/$SPY_DER_REF^{commit}" >/dev/null; then
+            SPY_TARGET="origin/$SPY_DER_REF"
+        fi
+    fi
+    git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" reset --hard "$SPY_TARGET"
+    echo "SPY-DER commit: $(git -C "$SPY_DER_DIR" rev-parse --short HEAD)"
+    "$APP_DIR/venv/bin/pip" install --quiet -e "$SPY_DER_DIR"
+else
+    log "SPY-DER parallel track disabled (SPY_DER_ENABLED=$SPY_DER_ENABLED)"
+fi
+
 log "systemd unit"
 install -m 644 "$APP_DIR/deploy/$SVC.service" "/etc/systemd/system/$SVC.service"
 systemctl daemon-reload
